This paper is primarily focused on image style transfer, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new approach that learns the transformation matrix with a feed-forward network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed approach on video style transfer, which could be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
